{"tid":388106,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"16歲少年屯門墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-09-05T08:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T08:20:15.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8609f3b8d3d4b9c66b42e0c1f3527a4f19f0f01c","tid":388106,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170905/57170314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170905%2F57170314&d=AA1KCNrHYCdSNSZN7dlTNqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=4f3e44ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170905%2F57170314&h=91d959e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170905/57170314</a><br />\n<br />\n【15:10 更新】墮樓少年為「星之子陳易希」的師弟，在學成績優異，曾多次奪得獎項，學校對事件感到惋惜。<br />\n<br />\n屯門青山公路新墟段玫瑰花園，凌晨零時許，16歲姓文少年，從大廈高處墮下，壓毀停在路邊的貨櫃拖頭車頂，再反彈跌落駕駛室與貨櫃之間位置，重傷昏迷，由救護員趕至送院搶救，惟終告不治。<br />\n警方經初步調查，在現場撿獲遺書，內容大概指父母不要怪責自己。據悉，死者為父母的獨子，早前曾透露有不開心，但未有道明為何事而不開心。<br />\n死者生前在屯門一中學就讀中五，為「星之子陳易希」的師弟，學校對事件亦感到惋惜。"},{"pid":"6bf841b1a128848536b5338c769af23af690e98e","tid":388106,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:08:16.000Z","msg":"據了解，文有先天性疾病，在母親懷孕期間，左手被臍帶纏繞著，血液難以暢順流通，故出生後左手短小無力。文在學成績優異，並醉心於發明，曾多次在科技項目中奪獎，如微型震動機械人比賽、少年兒童發明獎等等。他於2015年，亦與同學代表學校參加港燈舉辦的賽事，他們利用手推車開發了一台「便攜式能源教室」，奪得冠軍。同年，代表學校參加小科學家科技發明創意比賽，他們發明的醒目手扙亦奪得組別冠軍。<br />\n於2016年，文亦參加香港黏多醣症暨罕有遺傳病互助小組舉辦的賽事，其發明的「省力開瓶器」取得評判的一致讚賞，該小組副主席馬先生指，文發明的開瓶器好實用，他印象中，文表現聰明，態度積極，不明白文為何會選擇輕生，因此對事件表示非常難過及惋惜。"},{"pid":"059313cbab1cfa7f2ed33eb69b309aa38729f765","tid":388106,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170905/large/1504550879_8f4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170905%2Flarge%2F1504550879_8f4d.jpg&h=dd24d310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n墮樓男子跌墮拖頭尾部，警員在現場調查。(唐家輝攝)"},{"pid":"94387a235f23609f94294b248f954603377a5b4a","tid":388106,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:10:42.000Z","msg":"尖子呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就少咁個聰明仔"},{"pid":"9f8a445131e147cda05dae591da83b8197885bf6","tid":388106,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:11:05.000Z","msg":"關條柒頭咩事, 死左都要同人比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正垃圾妓者"},{"pid":"eea4c52a3a0f4735fcd04a4823e37f5d1a5a7f61","tid":388106,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:13:55.000Z","msg":"屌你<br />\n第一段 仲心諗以為陳生死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe4a019af27cde780640948a03ca1b979454c6e","tid":388106,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"私樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1fd0a049d070fcf26c8e8fb1a6de72737d77a2","tid":388106,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:20:15.000Z","msg":"貨櫃佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}